      "acceptanceCriteria": "Systematic comparison of at least two turbulence model forms (e.g. k-omega SST vs. RSM) for hemolysis-relevant shear stress predictions.",
      "rationale": "Only k-omega SST evaluated; alternative model form comparison not performed. Model form uncertainty uncharacterised at MRL 5 — flagged as significant epistemic gap."
