      "acceptanceCriteria": "Probability distributions assigned to all uncertain input parameters; sensitivity analysis identifies dominant contributors to NIH prediction uncertainty.",
      "rationale": "Monte Carlo sampling performed over inlet flow rate, rotational speed, and fluid viscosity. Hemolysis power-law exponent and coefficient treated as fixed nominal values; their uncertainty not propagated. Sensitivity analysis incomplete."
